  "notes": "Astell Scientific is a British manufacturer with a team possessing over 100 years of combined experience in sterilization equipment. They excel at creating compact, space-efficient designs that fit into facilities with limited floor space while maintaining high performance. Their media prep autoclaves are particularly useful for cosmetic manufacturers who need to sterilize formulation media, buffers, and aqueous solutions. Astell offers excellent customization capabilities, allowing them to design specialized solutions for unique sterilization requirements. Their equipment is known for economical running costs and simple maintenance, making them an excellent choice for facilities of all sizes seeking British engineering quality."
